      <title>澳大利亚3月份商业状况稳定，价格压力缓解</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/australia-business-conditions-steady-march-price-pressures-ease-2024-04-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二的一项调查显示，3月份澳大利亚商业状况几乎没有变化，尽管面对十年来的高利率，销售和就业保持稳定，而价格压力从高位略有缓解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/australia-business-conditions-steady-march-price-pressures-ease-2024-04-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 01:36:21 GMT</pubDate>
